{"tid":2427232,"cid":8,"subCid":0,"title":"入嚟傾下群體穿越番","createTime":"2021-02-28T15:47:17.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-03T03:53:24.000Z","uid":35136,"like":1,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":42,"replies":[{"pid":"8be8bce41f3ca7f2570bf76c87c245803f01fe60","tid":2427232,"uid":35136,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:47:17.000Z","msg":"而家穿越番泛濫 穿到冇咩新意<br />\n但群體穿越都係比較冷門<br />\n但我覺得通常群體穿越番有趣啲<br />\n一開頭可以描寫多啲現世界人去到異世界嘅不協調<br />\n一大班人唔同嘅價值觀又會有分歧而分黨分派<br />\n主角光環可以弱少少 唔使做萬能百科全書 有唔同配角擔任唔同角色<br />\n(領袖 咩都識嘅天才 運動健將 志願做醫生嘅補師 etc)<br />\n通常會送一橦建築 有一堆現代素材可以用<br />\n所以可以發揮嘅空間好大 <br />\n不過呢類作品唔係好多<br />\n我睇過都係漂流教室<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/14Y8e4A.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F14Y8e4A.jpg&h=36f8c0fe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n同群青戰記<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bh2MMbk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fbh2MMbk.jpg&h=1d6393c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n有冇巴絲打有推介<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91b3a8b73805ce705b18f3ab81726d270a617ea7","tid":2427232,"uid":2419,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:49:27.000Z","msg":"咁多穿越去異世界 反而想睇多d異世界穿越過黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f564dae427d903841cdc9d8cb0a4e64d2c149437","tid":2427232,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:49:38.000Z","msg":"刀劍？"},{"pid":"d98a21bfb9f3c3609ca834770b469c73e2b5e043","tid":2427232,"uid":299548,"like":9,"dislike":5,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"f564dae427d903841cdc9d8cb0a4e64d2c149437","tid":2427232,"uid":180124,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:49:38.000Z","msg":"刀劍？"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-02-28T15:50:18.000Z","msg":"世界第一<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\